{"article_id":"tWkII651yu90Q5Iy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Reid is furious","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that Republicans have thwarted the president 's nominations .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"|","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"AP Photos","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Senate goes for 'nuclear option '","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The Senate approved a historic rules change on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"by eliminating the use of the filibuster on all presidential nominees except those to the U.S. Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Invoking the long-threatened \" nuclear option \" means that most of President Barack Obama ' s judicial and executive branch nominees no longer need to clear a 60-vote threshold","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to reach the Senate floor","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and get an up-or-down vote .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Speak","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"ng at the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"bama praised the Senate action ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"ccusing Republicans of attempting to block his nominees","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"ased on politics alone , not on the merits of the nominee .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"This isn ' t obstruction on substance , on qualifications .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"t ' s just to gum up the works , \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"e said .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"enate Majority Leader Harry Reid","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"D-Nev. )","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"sed the nuclear option Thursday morning ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"eaning he called for a vote","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"o change the Senate rules by a simple majority vote .","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"t passed , 52 to 48 .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"hree Democrats voted against changing the rules","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Sen. Carl Levin of Michigan , Joe Manchin of West Virginia and Mark Pryor of Arkansas .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"It ' s time","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"o change the Senate","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"efore this institution becomes obsolete , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"eid said in a lengthy floor speech on Thursday morning .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"furious Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"R-Ky. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"ho tried to recess the Senate for the day","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"efore the rules change could get a vote ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"aid","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"fter the minority ' s power was limited by Democrats :","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"his is a time","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"o be talking about reprisal .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"think","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"t ' s a time","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"o be sad about what has been done to the United States Senate . \"","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"ut McConnell quickly noted","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"hat Republicans could fix the problem in the upcoming midterm elections","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"f they regain the majority :","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"The solution to this problem is an election .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"he solution to this problem is at the ballot box .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"e look forward to having a great election on 2014 . \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"he debate over the filibuster","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"and specifically its use on D.C . Circuit nominees -","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"as been raging for nearly a decade ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"tretching back to when George W. Bush was president","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"nd Democrats were in the minority .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"ut changing the Senate rules has always been avoided through a piecemeal deal , a gentleman ' s agreement or a specific solution , not a historic change to the very fabric of the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"ut since Obama ' s nomination , the \" nuclear option \" has reared its head three times in less than a year -","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"ach time getting closer to the edge .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"any in the Senate privately expected","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"hat this go-round would be yet another example of saber rattling ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"ut Reid said","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"ressure was increasing within his own party","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"o change the rules .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he blockade of three consecutive nominees to a powerful appellate court was too much for Democrats to handle","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and Reid felt compelled to pull the trigger ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"xplaining","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"hat \" this is the way","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"t has to be . \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"t didn ' t take long for Republicans to begin circulating both Reid ' s and Obama ' s past statements","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"pposing a rules change .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"ut the majority leader said","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"hat things escalated to a level","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"hat even he had not thought possible in 2005 ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"hen a \" Gang of 14 \" banded together","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"o stop a rules change .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"They have done everything","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"hey can","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"o deny the fact","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"hat Obama has been elected","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"nd then reelected , \"","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"e said .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"I have a right","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"o change how I feel about things . \"","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Earlier on :","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"ourt nominees :","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"attleground for partisan politics )","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"enate Democrats were quick to use their newfound powers ,","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"oting in the early afternoon","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"o end the filibuster on Patricia Millett ' s nomination to the D.C . Circuit Court of Appeals .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"he vote was 55-43 ,","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"ith two senators","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"oting present .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"efore the change earlier Thursday , Millett would have needed 60 votes","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"o clear the procedural hurdle","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"nd move on to a confirmation vote .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"ut now , she needed just 51","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"o advance .","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"n his speech , Obama noted","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"hat in the few decades","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"efore he took office ,","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"bout 20 nominees were filibustered .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"ince he took office ,","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"lose to 30 judicial and political nominees have had their nominations blocked .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"It ' s no secret","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"hat the American people have probably never been more frustrated with Washington ,","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"nd one of the reasons","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"hy that is ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"s that over the past five years , we ' ve seen an unprecedented pattern of obstruction in Congress","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"hat ' s prevented too much of the American people ' s business from getting done , \"","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"bama said .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Today ' s pattern of obstruction just isn ' t normal .","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"e can ' t allow it to become normal . \"","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"bama also cited the filibuster of a gun control bill earlier this year ,","depth":3},{"id":111,"text":"lthough Thursday ' s rule change would preserve the filibuster for Supreme Court picks and legislation .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":206,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration